  "short_description": "Popcorn Fever is a suika game featuring popcorns! Need a coffee break, stuck in a long commute, or just want to pass the time? Aim, drop, and merge the popcorns to score points. Customize your game by unlocking surprising powers. Find your own style and climb the leaderboard!",
