  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/7403972811bb18ffb01f627c7b115ecd.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=333 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/aad9092f144ac92370c24936ae4f9ce7.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Need a coffee break, stuck in a long commute, or just want to pass the time? Start a game and merge as many popcorns as you can! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aim, drop, and merge</strong> the popcorns to score points. <strong>Customize your game</strong> by unlocking unique and surprising powers. Find your own style and climb the <strong>leaderboard</strong>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you reach the top of the best player pantheon?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/ff4af78a27374b8350e3371bb91b2c08.poster.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/ff4af78a27374b8350e3371bb91b2c08.webm?t=1763389966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/db60e0c107289dd1dbfffea9970c65a1.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/077a9f3e469236c33df66336d611c1dc.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal is simple! Merge two identical popcorns to combine them and score points. The larger the popcorns, the more points they are worth. Drop the popcorns in the desired spot by moving your character and use physics to your advantage! There are 11 cute symbols to discover throughout your games. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Swap</strong>: You can swap your active symbol with the next symbol at any time! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combo</strong>: Chaining merges increases the point multiplier thanks to the Combo counter! If a dropped symbol doesn’t quickly create a merge, the points from the combo counter are collected.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/4bbbcbdbc31b2df33538dd8956e3d5a8.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/530a11eb003c413cc7ec08b5d8ba24e3.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can choose your powers through the shop; there are 9 powers to discover. Powers charge up through popcorn merges. When the countdown reaches 0, they are ready to be used. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hatching</strong>: All kernels turn into “Normy” popcorn! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/24dd0dd3b090a2628116f7f357174fcd.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shake</strong>: The bag shakes from left to right to help you create new merges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/d5b3cb1062c7a6e1427bb4f8916f193e.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Poppy Rain</strong>: It rains kernels! This is your chance to create many merges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/7ad8cf05fa113d11db1b6688f4c37d80.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combo x2</strong>: Doubles the points from the combo counter!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/ce7a67b67ab80074d5541879fcce57ab.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Payday</strong>: Goldy himself appears in your game! Use it for free, enjoy! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/0e56b644afdd55e9cc28e983845775cd.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bomb</strong>: The bomb is lit, and when dropped, it explodes and destroys nearby symbols. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/7bad0a5301b63bd127a4b226b36e9900.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fireball</strong>: The fireball is uncontrollable; it bounces around and destroys the symbols it touches before disappearing. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/0ee9cbf9d8709141e0ba628401a3f646.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Magician</strong>: Powerful but random, the magician upgrades several symbols. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/a2b0c9de7052b00e2187b4e50d6e44d5.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Joker</strong>: Small but mighty, the joker popcorn evolves the first symbol it touches.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/edf5ca1788374b546c0eb40521e23706.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/2436251a551b930cc1b6577d511ac364.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/86a55fd56afdf08b4727616429a13de9.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can purchase items to customize your character, the bag, or the wallpaper during games.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also choose to equip your 2 favorite powers. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/d01e730ff93a830f34d1b439844f3501.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/1c9bcca2d0a19771827a6f2045440a94.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 2 leaderboards, your personal best scores and the global leaderboard of the day, week, month, or all-time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/def645324fd76f5ef6a6343d4ff5e7de.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your character’s popcorn rotates automatically; sometimes you need to wait for the right moment to place the symbol wisely!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The kernel, “Poppy,” is small but dense, allowing it to sneak everywhere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merging 2 god popcorns reveals a surprise, can you discover it?</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/7403972811bb18ffb01f627c7b115ecd.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=333 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/aad9092f144ac92370c24936ae4f9ce7.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Need a coffee break, stuck in a long commute, or just want to pass the time? Start a game and merge as many popcorns as you can! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aim, drop, and merge</strong> the popcorns to score points. <strong>Customize your game</strong> by unlocking unique and surprising powers. Find your own style and climb the <strong>leaderboard</strong>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you reach the top of the best player pantheon?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/ff4af78a27374b8350e3371bb91b2c08.poster.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/ff4af78a27374b8350e3371bb91b2c08.webm?t=1763389966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/db60e0c107289dd1dbfffea9970c65a1.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste