ass=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/0ee9cbf9d8709141e0ba628401a3f646.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Magician</strong>: Powerful but random, the magician upgrades several symbols. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/a2b0c9de7052b00e2187b4e50d6e44d5.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Joker</strong>: Small but mighty, the joker popcorn evolves the first symbol it touches.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/edf5ca1788374b546c0eb40521e23706.avif?t=1763389966\" width=218 height=218 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/2436251a551b930cc1b6577d511ac364.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/86a55fd56afdf08b4727616429a13de9.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can purchase items to customize your character, the bag, or the wallpaper during games.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also choose to equip your 2 favorite powers. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035090/extras/d01e730ff93a830f34d1b439844f3501.avif?t=1763389966\" width=616 height=223 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" s